## Expected Impact

The long-term vision of this research is to move surveillance systems from reactive detection to proactive threat anticipation.

By identifying suspicious behavioral patterns before criminal actions occur, the proposed system may contribute to:

- Public safety
- Smart city initiatives
- Crime prevention strategies
- Decision support systems for security professionals

